title: Mod Selection Controls (lists)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

''<span class="term">Z, Enter, or Mouse Click</span>'' - Jump to a mod you have installed (mod list), or start a selected encounter (encounter list).

''<span class="term">X or left/right Shift</span>'' - Close the list.

''<span class="term">Up and Down, Mouse Scroll, Click and Drag</span>'' - Move up and down through the list.